<b>1.Installing Rails</b><br>
install <b>ruby sqlite3 gem</b> firstly and then<br>
<b>$ gem install rails</b><br><br>

<b>2.Create App</b><br>
(a)$ rails new xxx
(b)$ rails server    
(c)http://localhost:3000

<b>3.Say "Hello",Rails</b><br>
(a)$ rails generate controller welcome index
(b)$ vi app/views/welcome/index.html.erb

<b>4.Setting Home Page</b><br>
(a)$ vi config/routes.rb


<b>5 Getting Up and Running</b><br>
(a)$ vi config/routes.rb
<b>resources :xxxs(PLURAL STYLE)
(b)$ rails g controller xxxs
(c)$ vi app/controllers/articles_controller.rb
(d)$ vi views/articles/new.html.erb

